public class NavigationCriteria
extends _NavigationCriteria
    An ExpansionCriteria consists of a list of ConfigSpecs used to resolve masters to iterations, and a collection of Filters used in filtering Product Structures. ExpansionCriteria can be shared to other users.

    Use the newNavigationCriteria static factory method(s), not the NavigationCriteria constructor, to construct instances of this class. Instances must be constructed using the static factory(s), in order to ensure proper initialization of the instance.
